The paper focuses on developing a scalable visualization system for exploring large graph datasets, which involves database management (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), and data structures (cs.DS). The system is also designed to be interactive and user-friendly, which relates to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
